      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under formal version control with documented release notes and regression test suite covering relevant flow physics.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional license management with documented version control. Regression test suite covering rotating machinery and non-Newtonian viscosity models executed prior to study commencement. All tests passed within specified tolerances."
