      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verification against analytical benchmark cases for rotating flow and non-Newtonian viscosity must demonstrate errors below 5%.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed using Taylor-Couette flow benchmark and Hagen-Poiseuille flow with Carreau-Yasuda viscosity model. Numerical errors in velocity and wall shear stress fields were below 2.8% against analytical solutions, satisfying the 5% threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
