      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation applied to three systematically refined meshes. GCI for shear stress scalar and velocity magnitude fields below 3.2% at all five CPB operating points. Asymptotic range of convergence confirmed (apparent order of accuracy 1.94)."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with sufficient detail to permit replication in the CFD boundary conditions, including fluid properties, rotational speed, and flow rates.",
      "rationale": "FDA bench test conditions documented in Morrison et al. (2016) and supplementary data release. Fluid temperature, hematocrit, rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), and volumetric flow rates (3–7 L/min) all replicated in CFD boundary conditions within measurement uncertainty bounds."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
