      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all operating points, with RH < 1 criterion satisfied.",
      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against experimental values at all five operating points. Maximum discrepancy 11.3%. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed at all conditions, satisfying the predicate device comparison acceptance criterion."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
