      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump — the identical geometry used in the COU. Bovine blood surrogate fluid properties matched to human blood within documented uncertainty. Operating envelope of 3–7 L/min and 2000–3500 RPM encompasses all five COU operating points."
    },
    {
