      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; solver error subsumed within discretization error quantification.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, separate quantification of numerical solver error beyond discretization error is not required. Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms (all below 1e-5) and flux imbalance (below 0.01%) as standard practice."
    },
    {
