      "rationale": "Simulation setup documented in a controlled simulation plan reviewed by a second qualified CFD analyst. Boundary condition application and post-processing scripts version-controlled. Formal use error assessment not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
