      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; model form uncertainty acknowledged qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on literature consensus for rotating machinery hemolysis simulations. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) applied consistently with published CPB CFD literature. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
