      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; input uncertainty addressed through sensitivity analysis of key parameters.",
      "rationale": "Sensitivity of NIH predictions to viscosity model parameters and inlet velocity profile assessed qualitatively. Variations of ±10% in Carreau-Yasuda parameters produced NIH changes below 4%, confirming low sensitivity. Formal probabilistic input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
    },
